        {
            "title": "比亞迪在亞洲熱賣 戰爭推高油價並增強電動汽車吸引力",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 馬尼拉金融區的一家比亞迪汽車經銷店近來生意火爆，Matthew Dominique Poh稱，僅過去兩周他就接到了相當於一個月的訂單量。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「由於油價上漲，客戶紛紛用電動汽車替換燃油汽車，」在這家經銷店從事銷售工作七個月的Poh說。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"3月12日，菲律賓Makati市一個展廳內的比亞迪汽車攝影：尼爾·傑羅姆·莫拉萊斯/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PGr7i_jFwKwMDh1Yu3JhGQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ce2e6d9f5534849a6272009b9fe70e21\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">3月12日，菲律賓Makati市一個展廳內的比亞迪汽車攝影：尼爾·傑羅姆·莫拉萊斯/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">而在大約1770公里之外的河內，Nguyen Hoang Tu Anh表示，由於客戶到訪量成長了三倍，他經營的VinFast展廳不得不增聘銷售人員，並在伊朗戰爭爆發後的三周裡賣出了250輛電動汽車。這意味著每周銷量超過80輛，是2025年平均速度的兩倍。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-23122400-251c-3464-84f9-36991f311f4d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「改用電動汽車將幫助我們省下不少錢，」41歲的電信公司員工Lai The Manh Linh說道。他把燒油的豐田威馳小型車換成了一輛全新的純電動VinFast 5緊湊型跨界車，用於每天60-70公里的通勤。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管汽車製造商們尚未公佈3月（海灣衝突爆發後的首個整月）銷售數據，但早期跡象表明，中國比亞迪和越南VinFast等亞洲電動汽車製造商正在受益於油價飆升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">太平洋地區尤其能體會到油價上漲的痛苦。因為通過霍爾木茲海峽運輸的原油通常約80%會運往該地區，而現在中東衝突導致這一路線實際上走不通了。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"停放在河內VinFast展廳外的電動汽車攝影：Linh Pham/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OjGA16IYEvyLDepOizwe4w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8d5e1eb689e9c369affbb659aebedc58\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">停放在河內VinFast展廳外的電動汽車攝影：Linh Pham/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">亞洲開發銀行首席經濟學家Albert Park稱：「油價上漲從來都有利於朝電動汽車轉型。它能創造加快這一綠色轉型的經濟動機。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據彭博新能源財經的模型，全球普及電動汽車在去年幫助避免了相當於每天230萬桶原油的消耗。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題BYD Showrooms Are Bustling Across Asia After Iran Oil Shock</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Anuchit Nguyen、Ainsley Thomson、Peter Vercoe、Ishika Mookerjee、Kevin Dharmawan.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9E%E8%BF%AA%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E7%86%B1%E8%B3%A3-%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E6%8E%A8%E9%AB%98%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%A6%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%B7%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%B1%BD%E8%BB%8A%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E5%8A%9B-235314898.html",
